Four torrents of lightning."},{"lineNumber":35273,"originalJapaneseLine":"膨大な熱量が、即席の砦も周辺を固めていた魔軍も、","translatedEnglishLine":"The immense heat shattered both the makeshift fortress and the demon army surrounding it."},{"lineNumber":35274,"originalJapaneseLine":"その悉くを打ち砕いた。","translatedEnglishLine":"It destroyed every single one of them."},{"lineNumber":35275,"originalJapaneseLine":"「まったく、騒々しいの……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good grief, how noisy...\""},

{"lineNumber":35276,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……これほどのものが集まるか。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Is it possible for so much power to gather?"},

{"lineNumber":35277,"originalJapaneseLine":"　雷精が酔うておるかのようじゃ」","translatedEnglishLine":"It’s as if the thunder spirits are drunk.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35278,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん。特大の雷、四重奏。流石にぶっ飛んだね」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm. A massive thunder, fourfold. Truly amazing.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35279,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……こういうのも、悪くはねェもんだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...This kind of thing isn’t too bad either.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35280,"originalJapaneseLine":"「げほっ、なんてぇ魔力、だっ……！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Geh, what kind of magic power is that...!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35281,"originalJapaneseLine":"　クソ、一人は魔人じゃねーかっ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Damn, one of them is a demon lord...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35282,"originalJapaneseLine":"「マックス将軍！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"General Max!"}, 

{"lineNumber":35283,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんかこっちに来てやがりますぜ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"He's coming this way!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35284,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あぁん？　何かじゃ分からねぇよ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh? I can’t tell what it is."}, 

{"lineNumber":35285,"originalJapaneseLine":"　敵なら潰せっての」","translatedEnglishLine":"If it’s an enemy, crush it.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35286,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えぇ、そうなんでやすが……！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-yes, but...!"}, 

{"lineNumber":35287,"originalJapaneseLine":"　10人かそこらの奴らが、突破してきて……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"About ten or so of them broke through...!"}, 

{"lineNumber":35288,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ンだとぉ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What!?!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35289,"originalJapaneseLine":"「見えた、敵将！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I see the enemy general!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35290,"originalJapaneseLine":"魔法か何かですり抜けでもしたかのように、","translatedEnglishLine":"As if slipping through by magic or something,"}, 

{"lineNumber":35291,"originalJapaneseLine":"魔物の出城深くまで、人類の部隊が入り込んでいた。","translatedEnglishLine":"the human troops had infiltrated deep into the monster's outpost."}, 

{"lineNumber":35292,"originalJapaneseLine":"「すっごい手並み。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What an incredible skill."}, 

{"lineNumber":35293,"originalJapaneseLine":"　最低限の手数でここまで来ちゃえたよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"They got this far with minimal moves.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35294,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん……あの人間たち……やる。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm... Those humans... impressive."}, 

{"lineNumber":35295,"originalJapaneseLine":"　敵陣の薄い所を、一発で通って……」","translatedEnglishLine":"They went straight through the weakest part of the enemy line...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35296,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うん。それは……慣れてるから！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah. That’s because we’re used to it!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35297,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こういう所はお手の物か。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You’re skilled in these kinds of places."}, 

{"lineNumber":35298,"originalJapaneseLine":"　お前と、お前の女たちに感謝だな」","translatedEnglishLine":"I thank you and your women.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35299,"originalJapaneseLine":"「っ、そ、そういう言い方はやめてって……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"St-stop saying it like that...!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35300,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さて、この辺でいいか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Alright, is this spot good?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35301,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああ。角度良し、射程良し……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah. Angle good, range good..."}, 

{"lineNumber":35302,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ブッ込む頃合いってやつだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"It’s the perfect time to strike.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35303,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あのう！　その話と、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Um! That story and,"}, 

{"lineNumber":35304,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ずっと吉川さんが私の腕を掴んでいるのに、","translatedEnglishLine":"Yoshikawa-san has been holding my arm the whole time,"}, 

{"lineNumber":35305,"originalJapaneseLine":"　関係はあるのでしょうか！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Are those related?!"}, 

{"lineNumber":35306,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……任せたわ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...I’ll leave it to you.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35307,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はい？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35308,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そらいくぜ！　毛利忍法…………！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Here we go! Mouri ninja technique...!"}, 

{"lineNumber":35309,"originalJapaneseLine":"　デンジャラスジャイアントスイングの術ーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"The Dangerous Giant Swing technique—!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35310,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ひゃ？　はわ！　はわわわわわ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hya? Hawa! Hawawawawa!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35311,"originalJapaneseLine":"　まままま、まわるーーーーーー」","translatedEnglishLine":"Sp-sp-spinning—!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35312,"originalJapaneseLine":"「好きにやらせるかよ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I’m not just going to let you do as you please!"}, 

{"lineNumber":35313,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こっちも防備を……」","translatedEnglishLine":"We need to prepare our defenses too—\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35314,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………ん？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Huh?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35315,"originalJapaneseLine":"「きゃわーーーーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Kyaaahhh!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35316,"originalJapaneseLine":"「………………は？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Huh?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35317,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………あっ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Ah.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":35318,"originalJapaneseLine":"目が合った。","translatedEnglishLine":"Our eyes met."}, 

{"lineNumber":35319,"originalJapaneseLine":"その、刹那。","translatedEnglishLine":"At that very instant."}, 

{"lineNumber":35320,"originalJapaneseLine":"砦が、爆裂した。","translatedEnglishLine":"The fortress exploded."}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 雷の、雨……否。雷の濁流が、四つ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thunder, rain... no. Four torrents of lightning.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 膨大な熱量が、即席の砦も周辺を固めていた魔軍も、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The immense heat shattered both the makeshift fortress and the demon army surrounding it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その悉くを打ち砕いた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It destroyed every single one of them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……これほどのものが集まるか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Is it possible for so much power to gather?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 雷精が酔うておるかのようじゃ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s as if the thunder spirits are drunk."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ん。特大の雷、四重奏。流石にぶっ飛んだね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm. A massive thunder, fourfold. Truly amazing."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……こういうのも、悪くはねェもんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...This kind of thing isn’t too bad either."
"Geh, what kind of magic power is that...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クソ、一人は魔人じゃねーかっ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damn, one of them is a demon lord..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんかこっちに来てやがりますぜ！」
「あぁん？　何かじゃ分からねぇよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh? I can’t tell what it is.
If it’s an enemy, crush it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 10人かそこらの奴らが、突破してきて……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: About ten or so of them broke through...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法か何かですり抜けでもしたかのように、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As if slipping through by magic or something,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物の出城深くまで、人類の部隊が入り込んでいた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the human troops had infiltrated deep into the monster's outpost.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最低限の手数でここまで来ちゃえたよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They got this far with minimal moves."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敵陣の薄い所を、一発で通って……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They went straight through the weakest part of the enemy line..."
"Yeah. That’s because we’re used to it!"
"You’re skilled in these kinds of places.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前と、お前の女たちに感謝だな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thank you and your women."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「っ、そ、そういう言い方はやめてって……！」
ブッ込む頃合いってやつだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s the perfect time to strike."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ずっと吉川さんが私の腕を掴んでいるのに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yoshikawa-san has been holding my arm the whole time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 関係はあるのでしょうか！」
デンジャラスジャイアントスイングの術ーーー！」
「ひゃ？　はわ！　はわわわわわ！
まままま、まわるーーーーーー」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I’m not just going to let you do as you please!
We need to prepare our defenses too—"
